Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:27.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}無情的宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:40.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你獨自聽到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:53.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我做了一個遙遠的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:56.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該放棄什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該決定什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}我算什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:01.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}該選擇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}早已經決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:04.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}有沒有做錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}對著神質問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我並非獨自一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:18.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你一直在身邊 對我伸出這雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}沒什麼好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:33.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}即便化為怪物也要完成願望
